      • addKnownDependenciesToClasspath

        public List<File> addKnownDependenciesToClasspath​(File parent)
        Method to add known dependencies found within a parent directory to the classpath(). An artifact artifactId-version.packaging is a known artifact if there is META-INF/artifactId-version.packaging.dependencies file on the classpath which contains the artifact's dependencies.
        Parameters:
        parent - The parent File to analyze.
        Returns:
        The List of Files added to the classpath().
